WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.639
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.639 --> 00:00:04.240
Well, we're going to take communion today.

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:07.671
I have some stuff on my heart to talk to you all about.

00:00:07.671 --> 00:00:17.268
He said to me, 'During this great revival that's about to take place, you are about to see something that you've never seen before.

00:00:17.268 --> 00:00:25.210
' When I was praying into the harvest, he showed me the glory cloud again.

00:00:25.210 --> 00:00:32.960
And he said, 'Brandon, you will see the glory cloud, but it won't happen very often.

00:00:32.960 --> 00:00:35.920
' He said, 'That's something that I did in the past.

00:00:35.920 --> 00:00:40.960
' But he said, 'Behold, I'm going to do all things new.

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:46.660
I am going to bring forth new rivers, new oases in the desert.

00:00:46.660 --> 00:00:50.960
' He said, 'There will be in the days ahead.

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:52.126
' Listen to me.

00:00:52.126 --> 00:00:53.680
This will bless you.

00:00:53.680 --> 00:01:02.800
In the days ahead, a great refreshing is coming to the ones that are dry.

00:01:02.800 --> 00:01:05.350
A great river is coming.

00:01:06.370 --> 00:01:19.840
And he showed me, he said, 'Brandon, whenever the healing revival and the tent revival started with Jack Coe and Oral Roberts and William Brandon and all them, they would pray for people—and A.

00:01:23.466 --> 00:01:23.795
A.

00:01:23.795 --> 00:01:29.234
Allen, they would pray for people—and you didn't see anybody falling out like they do now with the courtesy falls.

00:01:29.234 --> 00:01:33.280
A lot of people fall out.

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:39.759
You see a lot of that stuff and you wonder, 'Is this performance or is it authentic?

00:01:39.759 --> 00:01:42.720
' I have experienced the authentic.

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:51.620
But whenever we first saw the healing movement of the tent revival, you didn't see anybody falling in those tents.

00:01:51.620 --> 00:01:52.500
I didn't, at least.

00:01:52.500 --> 00:02:00.228
And when I watch the old revival, I go through and watch the old videos on YouTube that started with Kathryn Kuhlman.

00:02:03.219 --> 00:02:10.200
It looked like—from what I understand, from what I'm trying to pinpoint—and correct me if I'm wrong, any of you elders, if you saw people fall out in tent revivals, then I'm wrong.

00:02:10.620 --> 00:02:21.618
But the Lord showed me that that really started to take off during Kathryn Kuhlman and Benny Hinn and some of the others.

00:02:21.618 --> 00:02:27.360
And now it happens all the time; you see them pray for people, people fall out.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:36.080
And it was a wave, and then it was the holy laughter and the shaking, and all that happened with Rodney Howard-Browne, and that happened a lot in the '90s.

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:39.660
Then it went into the early 2000s and so on, right?

00:02:39.660 --> 00:02:46.800
So the Lord showed me, he said, 'Behold, I'm going to do something new.

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:52.569
' And I had an open-eyed vision, and he said, 'Brandon, I saw the glory cloud come in.

00:02:52.569 --> 00:02:59.040
' But he said, 'What is going to happen with this last outpouring, this last push?

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:03.519
' He said, 'I'm going to do something that you've never seen before.

00:03:03.519 --> 00:03:12.729
You need to start to think bigger, for what has been in the past will be something—I'm going to do something new.

00:03:12.729 --> 00:03:16.349
' And I saw this blonde-headed woman.

00:03:16.349 --> 00:03:21.040
And I saw some other people come down to the front of his meetings.

00:03:21.040 --> 00:03:33.461
And a tangible wind of the spirit of the Lord came in like a mighty rushing wind with cloven tongues of fire like it was in Acts chapter 2.

00:03:33.461 --> 00:03:39.570
And I'm talking—there's no way to explain what I saw; it doesn't make any sense.

00:03:43.150 --> 00:03:59.223
I saw wind blowing these women's hair like a whirlwind, and it was whipping their hair around and their clothes, and they actually could feel the wind of the spirit on them and they fell out that way.

00:03:59.223 --> 00:04:01.071
I saw a wind as you went.

00:04:01.071 --> 00:04:03.589
It was like the power of the Holy Spirit.

00:04:04.340 --> 00:04:17.280
It was like moving your hand, and I saw the glory moving in the atmosphere, and people could feel the wind of the Holy Spirit in the auditorium.

00:04:17.280 --> 00:04:26.720
And as the wind of the Holy Spirit moved through the auditorium, people were getting healed and their hair was actually tangibly moving.

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:30.640
And the Lord said, 'You've never seen what I'm about to do in these last days.

00:04:30.640 --> 00:04:38.960
' He said that before, when people would fall out, you had the people in the audience saying, 'Is that real?

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:39.200
Is that real?

00:04:39.200 --> 00:04:42.251
' with the holy laughter, if they're not experienced.

00:04:42.251 --> 00:04:54.240
But when you feel a tangible move of the Holy Spirit on you—like the glory cloud, everybody could sense it in Azusa Street.

00:04:54.240 --> 00:05:02.586
The glory cloud—they said they played with it as kids; it was a tangible, thick fog.

00:05:02.586 --> 00:05:09.280
And it even talks about it in the Bible; it filled the Holy of Holies.

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:26.627
But the Lord said to me, 'I'm going to do something new and it will be a refreshing, for my fragrance will fill the atmosphere whenever people are ministering.

00:05:26.627 --> 00:05:33.280
' He said, 'You will tangibly smell my fragrance, for I carry a fragrance.

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:40.199
' And it was a refreshing.

00:05:40.199 --> 00:05:50.106
When people breathe in this fragrance, the Lord said it will be like something you've never smelled—like heaven on earth.

00:05:50.106 --> 00:05:53.560
Breathing in, and you'll be physically healed.

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:57.380
It will be a wind of the spirit.

00:05:57.380 --> 00:06:05.440
I saw people being touched by the Shekinah glory in a different way than we've ever seen before.

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:12.720
He's going to do something like we've never seen before.

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:20.080
And I saw the wind whipping around people's hair and it was moving on them and they were being refreshed.

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:27.039
And old wineskins that had turned into vinegar turned into new wine.

00:06:27.039 --> 00:06:37.307
A new fragrance, a new presence of the Lord will be like an oasis in the days ahead on people in major services.

00:06:37.307 --> 00:06:45.129
And I'm telling you, they're coming from the north; I'm telling you, they're coming from the south; they're coming from the east; they're coming from the west.

00:06:45.129 --> 00:06:50.720
People are hungry and they're desperate for a move of God.

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:54.514
They're desperate for a fresh touch from the Lord.

00:06:54.514 --> 00:06:59.226
And I'm telling you, he said, 'My yoke is easy and my burden is light.

00:06:59.226 --> 00:07:04.400
Come unto me all ye that are heavy laden and I will give you rest.

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:07.737
' Do you understand what God is about to do?

00:07:07.737 --> 00:07:10.370
We've never seen it in generations past.

00:07:10.370 --> 00:07:18.960
We're going to see a fresh touch of the fire of the Holy Spirit on every single person who is thirsty.

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:24.674
Those that are hungry, he said he's going to give you fresh meat.

00:07:24.674 --> 00:07:35.039
Something new and tangible is coming and he's looking for an 'all hands on deck' experience who will just say yes.

00:07:35.039 --> 00:07:40.240
He said he would pour out his spirit upon all flesh.

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:48.045
And I believe right now we are at that place where he said, 'Brandon, it's time to become more active in fasting.

00:07:48.045 --> 00:07:52.537
It's time to become more in line with prayer and fasting.

00:07:52.537 --> 00:07:54.113
Pray and fast.

00:07:55.399 --> 00:07:59.680
Seek me daily and you will find me.

00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:03.662
' I said, 'Lord, I need a fresh touch.

00:08:03.662 --> 00:08:11.840
' Give me that living water and let it overflow.

00:08:11.840 --> 00:08:20.194
Not ministering to people out of your reserves, but ministering to my people out of the overflow of your heart.

00:08:20.194 --> 00:08:32.719
Out of the overflow to the extreme, to the full, until it overflows—out of your belly shall flow rivers of living water.

00:08:32.719 --> 00:08:42.000
And he told me, he said, 'That will come through fasting and prayer, seeking me daily, and you will find me.

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:51.897
' And out of this personal, more intimate relationship with me will become a greater overflow out of you for the people.

00:08:51.897 --> 00:08:58.880
But you'll not get there until you have intimacy even on a greater level with me.

00:08:58.880 --> 00:09:04.306
There's many of my ministers, he said, that are trying to minister out of their reserves.

00:09:04.306 --> 00:09:09.680
And many of them are ministering in a dry place.

00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:13.360
But he said, 'I want you to drink from my river.

00:09:13.360 --> 00:09:19.839
Drink from the well that never shall run dry.

00:09:19.839 --> 00:09:21.573
' Do you understand?

00:09:21.573 --> 00:09:25.040
'Fill my cup, Lord.

00:09:25.040 --> 00:09:27.760
I lift it up, Lord.

00:09:27.760 --> 00:09:29.337
' That's where he's at.

00:09:29.337 --> 00:09:32.920
And he told me, he said, 'He's uncapping those wells of revival.

00:09:32.920 --> 00:09:40.100
' And I told you what I saw about ORU and about what he's going to do with the students there on the ORU campus.

00:09:40.100 --> 00:09:50.029
And he said, 'I'm going to bring forth a great and mighty revival with this young generation, and it will be through the Mabee Center.

00:09:50.029 --> 00:09:52.422
And I'm going to fill that Mabee Center up.

00:09:52.422 --> 00:09:56.880
' And I'm telling you, it's not going to be a convenient move with people.

00:09:57.280 --> 00:10:01.279
It's time for my bedtime.

00:10:01.279 --> 00:10:02.959
We've seen it at our church.

00:10:02.959 --> 00:10:13.000
And people—we had probably five or six families that stayed, and the rest of the congregation left because it got too late for them.

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:19.040
How desperate are you?

00:10:19.040 --> 00:10:20.107
How hungry?

00:10:20.107 --> 00:10:24.320
How thirsty are you?

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:25.280
How hungry?

00:10:25.280 --> 00:10:26.240
How desperate?

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:32.228
How thirsty are you?

00:10:32.228 --> 00:10:37.529
Blessed are those that hunger and thirst after righteousness, for they will be filled.

00:10:55.176 --> 00:10:55.424
I tell you this because it's so important that you shake off the old you and get ready for what God is about to do.

00:10:55.424 --> 00:11:05.984
When you experience the true healing flow of the river of the Holy Spirit, there's no time.

00:11:14.267 --> 00:11:15.493
You can be there all night.

00:11:15.493 --> 00:11:22.319
Give me an alarm code; I'll turn it on.

00:11:22.319 --> 00:11:28.000
Give me a key; I did that for years.

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:31.040
I just want to sit at the feet of Jesus.

00:11:31.040 --> 00:11:32.480
Who cares about anything else?

00:11:32.480 --> 00:11:37.930
There's nothing else in this earth that I want other than to be a Holy Ghost junkie, you know.

00:11:37.930 --> 00:11:43.493
But I don't want to be addicted to a movement and not see people's lives changed.

00:11:43.493 --> 00:11:59.160
If we get a fresh drink—if we get it—we don't want to be Holy Ghost crack addicts and not get changed, letting it change us where we're getting a Holy Ghost high every time we come in there and we're not taking it out and dumping it out on the nations.

00:11:59.370 --> 00:12:12.240
You can either let it change you, or you can be a Holy Ghost crack addict and come from one high to another high to another high and you don't do anything with it.

00:12:12.240 --> 00:12:28.752
He's not touching you so you can just have your Holy Ghost goosebumps, take it home and don't change, and then you come back the next week and you have to be resurrected spiritually because you're spiritually dead again because you didn't take a day-to-day relationship with the Father.

00:12:30.480 --> 00:12:34.933
You only got a Holy Ghost infilling on Sunday, but the rest of the week you lived like hell.

00:12:37.499 --> 00:12:45.024
The Lord wants you to come unto him and be filled and controlled by the Holy Spirit every single day of your life to the overflow.

00:12:45.024 --> 00:12:55.440
He's touching you with the Holy Ghost and fire so that you can take it to the generation that's dying and thirsty.

00:12:55.440 --> 00:13:01.950
They need a fresh touch from Jesus, and he wants to give it to you so you can give it to them.

00:13:01.950 --> 00:13:08.447
Let your life be a light that shines unto all men, women, children, whoever.

00:13:08.447 --> 00:13:12.031
Let it flow up out of you, out of that river.

00:13:12.031 --> 00:13:21.413
But you look like you have to be raised from the dead when you come on Sunday because you've gone through and you haven't had intimacy with him all week.

00:13:21.413 --> 00:13:28.368
There's something more, and there's something wrong with a lot of it.

00:13:28.368 --> 00:13:36.520
I look at it and say, 'Man, I don't want to be the 25%.

00:13:38.900 --> 00:13:39.920
I want to be sitting at his feet.

00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:41.600
I'm desperate for him.

00:13:41.600 --> 00:13:44.011
I need a fresh touch from God.

00:13:44.011 --> 00:13:52.799
' And what we're about to see, 'If I be lifted up,' he said, 'I will draw all men unto me.

00:13:52.799 --> 00:13:54.999
' Who cares about popularity?

00:13:54.999 --> 00:13:56.800
Who cares about the finances?

00:13:56.800 --> 00:14:05.059
I do not care about how much money I'm going to get in the days ahead from investments.

00:14:05.059 --> 00:14:07.279
So what?

00:14:07.279 --> 00:14:09.680
What is it there for?

00:14:09.680 --> 00:14:15.720
What did he do it for you for?

00:14:15.720 --> 00:14:25.200
It wasn't for you to be stupid with it; it's so that you can help further the kingdom.

00:14:25.200 --> 00:14:26.640
Do you understand?

00:14:26.640 --> 00:14:27.657
He's coming.

00:14:27.657 --> 00:14:35.680
I've told you a thousand times, and there's so many of you that still don't get it.

00:14:35.680 --> 00:14:36.453
He's coming.

00:14:36.453 --> 00:14:40.199
Ladies and gentlemen, the King is standing at the door.

00:14:40.199 --> 00:14:42.453
The King is coming.

00:14:52.497 --> 00:14:52.692
The King is coming.

00:14:52.692 --> 00:14:55.199
Do you understand?

00:14:55.199 --> 00:14:55.703
He's coming.

00:14:55.703 --> 00:14:57.433
We're about to see signs in the heavens.

00:14:57.433 --> 00:14:59.920
We're about to see signs in the earth.

00:15:17.173 --> 00:15:17.439
It's not funny; it's serious.

00:15:17.439 --> 00:15:24.000
We're about to see some things that are going to shake to awake.

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:40.600
But are you going to be there with the catcher's mitts ready to receive the people when they're coming in and they're dry and they're thirsty and they're going, 'Man, I need somebody to help me'?

00:15:50.480 --> 00:15:50.860
Are you going to be the one that says come?

00:15:54.434 --> 00:16:00.160
Are you going to be the one that has the fire to say, 'I know the way.

00:16:08.400 --> 00:16:09.040
I know you're desperate.

00:16:11.399 --> 00:16:23.006
I know you're hurting, but I know a Jesus that will take care of all that for you if you just bow your knee to him and worship him today'?

00:16:23.006 --> 00:16:24.910
Does that make sense?

00:16:35.782 --> 00:16:36.193
It's going to take a person that's sold out, that's not worried about a time clock, about convenience.

00:16:36.193 --> 00:16:44.057
A revival, an awakening, is not going to be convenient for a lot of you.

00:16:44.057 --> 00:16:49.592
'Well, I didn't get to watch Friends today' or whatever.

00:16:49.592 --> 00:16:52.480
I don't know, whatever the latest thing is—probably not that.

00:16:52.480 --> 00:16:55.360
'I didn't get to watch my whatever.

00:16:55.640 --> 00:17:01.440
I need to go home, and I'd like to have my latte.

00:17:01.440 --> 00:17:04.550
' I'm talking about sold out.

00:17:04.550 --> 00:17:07.359
Are you sold out for Jesus today?

00:17:07.359 --> 00:17:09.439
Are you sold out?

00:17:09.439 --> 00:17:19.387
I have to tell you, it's time to just get to that point where you're just desperate, where there's nothing else that matters.

00:17:19.387 --> 00:17:25.800
I'm just saying I got so excited when I saw what he's about to do.

00:17:25.800 --> 00:17:42.160
When I saw all the people that were so broken and so downcast get a fresh touch from Jesus and see their faces changed by the power of the Holy Spirit.

00:17:42.160 --> 00:17:57.120
When you see that heaviness, and they feel that they're so lost, and then they finally have hope—that's what it's all about, showing them the way for what's about to come.

00:17:57.120 --> 00:18:05.200
Yeah, I've seen some dark things, darker than most, but I'm so focused on him.

00:18:05.200 --> 00:18:12.039
I want to be so precise that I don't miss anything that he has for me.

00:18:12.039 --> 00:18:20.559
I do not want to miss anything, and I will lack no good thing that he has for me.

00:18:20.559 --> 00:18:39.120
I said, 'Man, yes, there's a lot of pressure with leading this, but I will tell you this: there's nothing that can compare to sitting at his feet after you fast and you get in that vein.

00:18:39.120 --> 00:18:46.300
' And you go, 'What is it that is so easy?

00:18:46.300 --> 00:18:53.867
' Just denying the flesh, taking up the cross, and following him through inconvenience for hunger, inconvenience for what's convenient.

00:18:53.867 --> 00:18:59.120
I told my wife, we were talking about it, she said, 'Brandon, we're so desperate.

00:18:59.120 --> 00:19:03.771
We're so thirsty.

00:19:03.771 --> 00:19:07.360
We're so hungry for what he's about to do.

00:19:07.360 --> 00:19:11.920
' I want to be right in the center of it.

00:19:21.470 --> 00:19:21.820
I want to be on the front row of what he's doing and just sit there and soak it up.

00:19:22.170 --> 00:19:28.533
You know, fill my cup, Lord.

00:19:28.533 --> 00:19:31.839
I'm excited for what's coming, y'all.

00:19:31.839 --> 00:19:41.288
I have an anticipation for what I saw with the glorious outpouring of what he's about to do.

00:19:55.900 --> 00:19:56.320
A new thing, a new thing is coming.

00:20:12.251 --> 00:20:15.147
And excitement should be inside of you.

00:20:15.147 --> 00:20:15.609
Anticipation.

00:20:15.609 --> 00:20:21.169
Expectation will bring the manifestation of what you're believing God for.

00:20:21.169 --> 00:20:23.849
Expect God to do something big in your life.

00:20:24.124 --> 00:20:32.183
And whenever he does it, get ready to share it with your neighbor and tell everyone around you what God has done.

00:20:32.183 --> 00:20:36.240
He doesn't heal you just to heal you.

00:20:36.240 --> 00:20:41.147
He doesn't bring finances just so you can hoard it up.

00:20:41.147 --> 00:20:54.434
He does things in your life supernaturally to heal your body, to touch you, so that you can do something to tell people about what he's done.

00:20:54.434 --> 00:20:56.560
Look at the lepers.

00:20:56.560 --> 00:21:03.039
There was only one that came back to give Jesus thanks and say thank you.

00:21:03.039 --> 00:21:12.910
How many of you, whenever he touches your life for what you've been believing for all this time, will not go and give God the praise for what he's done?

00:21:12.910 --> 00:21:14.079
God, I worship you.

00:21:32.113 --> 00:21:32.548
Lord, you are good and your mercy endures forever.

00:21:32.548 --> 00:21:38.263
For the Lord, he is good and his mercy endures forever.

00:21:38.263 --> 00:21:40.274
He is worthy of all our praise.

00:21:40.274 --> 00:21:43.549
He is worthy of all our everything.

00:21:43.549 --> 00:21:47.591
God, you are so good and we just want to say thank you.

00:21:47.591 --> 00:21:50.880
Don't be the leper that doesn't come back and tell Jesus thank you.

00:21:51.520 --> 00:22:05.880
And don't be a doubting Thomas that—if Jesus was healing the sick today for what I'm seeing coming, would he tell you to leave the room because you have no faith to believe for what's about to take place?

00:22:05.880 --> 00:22:18.354
He'll have to bypass you and say, 'Listen, sister so-and-so, we need you to step outside because your faith is dampening the atmosphere.

00:22:18.354 --> 00:22:29.908
' Or would he say, 'You can stay because we know you know how to tug along and believe for big like he did at Jairus's house'?

00:22:42.410 --> 00:22:42.740
I refuse to be one that Jesus would have to say, 'Please leave the room.

00:22:42.740 --> 00:22:49.309
' I just want to be with him and say, 'Well done, thy good and faithful servant, Brandon.

00:22:49.309 --> 00:22:50.660
' You're doing it.

00:22:50.660 --> 00:23:09.412
You believe me for—I stagger not at the promise of God through unbelief, but am strong in faith, giving glory to God, being fully persuaded that what God has promised he's able also to perform it—that he's given one last call, ladies and gentlemen, for the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen.

00:23:09.412 --> 00:23:14.231
So we pray right now and we're going to lift up our president.

00:23:14.231 --> 00:23:23.319
We're going to lift up these meetings and we're going to give God praise for what he's about to do, ladies and gentlemen, in this earth.

00:23:31.733 --> 00:23:32.386
For it will be like waters covering the sea.

00:23:39.271 --> 00:23:39.769
It will be a Holy Ghost revival throughout this whole world and then the end will come.

00:23:39.769 --> 00:23:42.685
I'm telling you, a major outpouring.

00:23:42.685 --> 00:23:49.360
So, Father, I thank you, Lord, for you're going to give drink to the thirsty.

00:23:49.360 --> 00:23:51.520
You're going to give bread to the hungry.

00:23:58.693 --> 00:23:59.120
Father, I thank you, Lord, for those that are dry and thirsty that we come unto you.

00:24:15.988 --> 00:24:16.251
And we're not going to just do it and have a Holy Ghost shake out, but we're going to get filled and we're going to dump it all over those around us.

00:24:16.251 --> 00:24:22.217
Father, I know you touch those around us so that we can touch the nations for you.

00:24:22.217 --> 00:24:44.217
